OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784654323
OL,3,CMinister Lyons slams EU rules over
OL,4,C#850 VAT cut
OL,6,FAn #850million VAT axe on electricity
OL,7,Fbills that won't apply to Northern
OL,8,FIreland exposes "the nonsense of
OL,9,Frules" with the EU, a Stormont
OL,10,FMinister has said.
OL,12,FGordon Lyons hit out after new Prime
OL,13,FMinister Andy Burnham made the
OL,14,Fannouncement in a bid to ease the cost
OL,15,Fof living crisis saving households in
OL,16,FEngland, Scotland and Wales around #45
OL,17,Fa year.
OL,26,@pD@QOUqD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784654323
OL,3,CMinister Lyons slams EU rules over
OL,4,C#850 VAT cut
OL,6,FBut the Minister for Communities said
OL,7,Fbecause of post-Brexit rules under the
OL,8,FWindsor Framework, EU VAT rates apply
OL,9,Fon electricity bills here. Stormont
OL,10,Fwould be given funds to put special
OL,11,Fmechanisms in place in order to avail
OL,12,Fof a similar level of support.
OL,14,FThe DUP MLA for East Antrim added: "I
OL,15,Fhave been calling for cuts on tax and
OL,16,FVAT to help with the cost of living
OL,17,Fcrisis, something that could be done
OL,18,Fsimply and across the UK.
OL,26,@vD@dOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784654323
OL,3,CMinister Lyons slams EU rules over
OL,4,C#850 VAT cut
OL,6,F"But because of the rules that exist
OL,7,Fthat we're subject to under the
OL,8,FWindsor Framework, it means that we're
OL,9,Fnot able to benefit in the same way.
OL,11,F"Now, the Government have said that
OL,12,Fthey're going to give us money, but we
OL,13,Fdon't have the mechanism. We will need
OL,14,Fto put that in place, and that will
OL,15,Fcause delay.
OL,17,F"So, I'm disappointed that the
OL,18,Fgovernment, on this first initiative
OL,19,Fthat they have announced, haven't
OL,20,Freally taken Northern Ireland into
OL,21,Fconsideration.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784654323
OL,3,CMinister Lyons slams EU rules over
OL,4,C#850 VAT cut
OL,6,F"This is a Prime Minister who said he
OL,7,Fwas concerned about devolution and the
OL,8,Fregions of the UK. But what he needs
OL,9,Fto actually do is go negotiate with
OL,10,Fthe European Union so that we can
OL,11,Fbenefit from this.
OL,13,F"And doesn't it show the nonsense of
OL,14,Fthe rules that we have with the EU,
OL,15,Fthat we can't get the same VAT
OL,16,Freduction as everybody else in the
OL,17,Frest of the UK will get, without
OL,18,Fhaving to go through a difficult
OL,19,Fprocess that's going to take longer?
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784654323
OL,3,CMinister Lyons slams EU rules over
OL,4,C#850 VAT cut
OL,6,F"We've heard lots of rhetoric from the
OL,7,Fnew Prime Minister and his team. I
OL,8,Fwant to see results. I want to make
OL,9,Fsure that we get real delivery for
OL,10,Fpeople in Northern Ireland. That will
OL,11,Frequire him to think differently than
OL,12,Fwhat has happened already.
OL,14,F"Something very simple could have been
OL,15,Fdone that everybody would have
OL,16,Fbenefited from straight away: a cut on
OL,17,Fthe tax and VAT on oil or on fuel duty
OL,18,Fwould have been something that people
OL,19,Fcould have felt immediately.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784654323
OL,3,CMinister Lyons slams EU rules over
OL,4,C#850 VAT cut
OL,6,F"And it would have had long-lasting
OL,7,Fconsequences as well, because reducing
OL,8,Fa fuel duty, as an example, doesn't
OL,9,Fjust mean that you see that price
OL,10,Freduced at the pump; everything that's
OL,11,Fmoved and shipped and transported
OL,12,Fbetween and within the United Kingdom
OL,13,Fwould have had the benefit from that
OL,14,Fas well, and would have had knock-on
OL,15,Fconsequences.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784654323
OL,3,CMinister Lyons slams EU rules over
OL,4,C#850 VAT cut
OL,6,F"The last government under Keir
OL,7,FStarmer failed to do that. Here's an
OL,8,Fopportunity for Andy Burnham. I
OL,9,Fbelieve that he wants to help out, I
OL,10,Fbelieve that he wants to ease the cost
OL,11,Fof living pressures. There's very
OL,12,Fstraightforward and easy ways in which
OL,13,Fhe can do that, and unfortunately he
OL,14,Fhasn't done it in this circumstance
OL,15,Ffor Northern Ireland."
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
OL,20,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,21,Fhere.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/7
